adviseScripts.text: Why are you just staring at me?

adviseScripts.text: Why would they do that to me?

adviseScripts.text: Could just be their personality.
They want to keep a certain distance between them and their subordinates.

adviseScripts.text: I had thought I was doing something wrong.
adviseScripts.speaker: Isabel

adviseScripts.text: But...
adviseScripts.speaker: Isabel

adviseScripts.text: After all we've been through together, is there still a need to keep our distance?

adviseScripts.text: Everyone in Eden is like this...

adviseScripts.text: Darling,
adviseScripts.speaker: Isabel

adviseScripts.text: every single thing I do,
adviseScripts.speaker: Isabel

adviseScripts.text: I hope you can understand that.

adviseScripts.text: If only there was one more of you, I could hide the other you in a safe, secret place and love you forever.

... You are so gentle and kind.

adviseScripts.text: Is that so?

adviseScripts.speaker: Isabel

adviseScripts.text: You and I were destined to be together.

adviseScripts.text: My feelings are... a little different from yours.
adviseScripts.speaker: Isabel

adviseScripts.text: I talk with Isabel about the value of marriage.

adviseScripts.text: Tell me something about you. Anything.

adviseScripts.text: I graduated from a military academy.
There's nothing I love more than a blue sky.

adviseScripts.text: I envy him.

adviseScripts.text: *Sigh*

adviseScripts.speaker: Isabel

adviseScripts.text: Just say the word, and I'll take care of whatever, or whoever, it is.
adviseScripts.speaker: Isabel

adviseScripts.text: You poor soul.

adviseScripts.text: With you, on a day like this...

adviseScripts.text: Going on a trip with you...
adviseScripts.speaker: Isabel

adviseScripts.text: Oh, how I have longed for this day!
adviseScripts.speaker: Isabel

adviseScripts.text: It's finally coming true!
adviseScripts.speaker: Isabel

adviseScripts.text: That would work too, but
adviseScripts.speaker: Isabel

adviseScripts.speaker: Isabel

adviseScripts.text: Or is that just a pipe dream?

Honey.

adviseScripts.text: Take a sip.
Don't drink.
My vision started to blur.
Are you all right?

adviseScripts.text: I think so.
Oh... you are?

adviseScripts.text: ... Darn.
adviseScripts.speaker: Isabel

adviseScripts.text: Just one sip! Is that so hard?

adviseScripts.speaker: Isabel

adviseScripts.text: Maybe next time.

If it were a special occasion and
adviseScripts.speaker: Isabel

adviseScripts.text: you wanted to celebrate it with someone,
adviseScripts.speaker: Isabel

adviseScripts.text: who would you want to be with?

adviseScripts.text: I'm so touched!
adviseScripts.speaker: Isabel

adviseScripts.text: You're not being serious, are you?
adviseScripts.speaker: Isabel

adviseScripts.text: That must be why you didn't sound so sure in your response, right?

adviseScripts.text: I nodded my head.
Phew... That's what I was hoping. Sorry, I guess I'm not used to your sense of humor yet.

adviseScripts.text: If you had been telling the truth, I was going to go bust some skulls. Namely those three girls!

adviseScripts.text: I'm glad you were only joking.

Cozy and with lots of woodwork.
